Teaching students how to be an advocate and ally 🏳️‍🌈 can be engaging and creative with this activity! #ad I teamed up with @michaelsstores to help you teach your student about the importance of advocacy.

Be sure to grab all of your favorite multi-colored and alphabet beads for kids at your local Michaels stores for this project with your students! #makeitwithmichaels

#michaelspartner #teachersofig #teachersofinstagram #iteachtoo #teachersofinsta #teachingadvocacy

node.text:
Printing art, classroom decor and instructional materials for my classroom makeovers is made possible using @staplesstores print and marketing services! I use their services every single time because the quality and sharpness of the prints is unmatched and the same-day pick up feature has truly saved me (hello, procrastination)!

I used Staples to print a series of motivational songs in record-format for the most recent classroom transformation and they were a huge hit!

Printing at Staples is easy:
✏️ Choose the art/decor you want to print.
✏️ Upload it to their printing services section online.
✏️ Pick up your order.
✏️ Display in your classroom!

#staples #workingandlearningstore #classroomdecor #classroomdesign #classroomideas #classroommakeover #iteachtoo #teachersofig #teachersofinstagram

node.text:
Hi ♥️

My favorite part about this journey so far is seeing MJ in action. She’s the most caring and warm person I know— especially when it comes to scooping up SJ. How did I get so lucky?! For real.

My least favorite part is the anxiety that if I’m not staring at him while he’s sleeping, something terrible will happen. 🤦🏻‍♀️ We tried doing shifts, but my brain won’t let me. We’re obviously practicing safe sleep and using the owlet, but ya know… that’s just me 😂.

But overall, we’re doing well and we love Sanford so much!

📸: @caitrosephotography

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Brittany Jeltema on September 05, 2021.

node.text:

node.text: First time holding SJ… in this moment all of my anxieties disappeared. Have no fear… they’re back in full force, but this is a memory I’ll never forget. 🥲

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Brittany Jeltema on August 31, 2021 tagging @m_jeltema10. May be an image of 2 people, baby and indoor.

node.text:
🍼 Sanford Lee Jeltema entered the world today at 2:55am! He’s a long 21” and 7 pounds 2 ounces.

MJ is a freaking rockstar. I am continuously in awe her and this experience has bonded us in a way I didn’t know was possible. She’s recovering ❤️‍🩹 like a beast and is feeling better than expected!

As I type this, I’m laying on this tiny cot in the hospital, running on 1 hour of sleep… but I’m staring at MJ and SJ, both resting their eyes peacefully… and all I can think about is the overwhelming feeling of love and adoration. The urge to protect is insurmountable, too… in a way that I’ve never experienced.

Thank you for letting me share about our lives in this tiny sliver of the internet. We love you and are grateful for your support. ♥️

#twomoms #lgbtqfamily #twomomsquad #loveislove #lovewins #gaygirlgang #welcometotheworld
